data.description: Unique property alert! This 2 bedroom 2 bathroom home is located just a stone throw away from the beautiful Feather River Fish Hatchery. Huge living room with cozy Fireplace! The Upstairs Bathroom has a Jetted tub perfect for soaking after a long day. There is a converted bonus space downstairs with heating and air and its own hot water heater to supply the full bathroom and sink in that bonus area. This bonus area could be perfect for storage, guests, or a home office. Please call your agent today for a showing!
